        "formula": "给定输入张量 p,t ∈ ℝ^{N×F}，其中 N=batch_size=128，F=input_shape[0]=4096。对每个样本 i∈[0,N-1]，定义点积 dot_i = Σ_{f=0}^{F-1} p[i,f]·t[i,f]，L2范数乘积 norm_product_i = (Σ_{f=0}^{F-1} p[i,f]^2)^{1/2}·(Σ_{f=0}^{F-1} t[i,f]^2)^{1/2}。余弦相似度 cos_sim_i = dot_i / (norm_product_i + ε)，其中 ε=1e-8（PyTorch cosine_similarity 默认 eps）。单样本损失 loss_i = 1 - cos_sim_i。最终输出标量 L = (1/N)·Σ_{i=0}^{N-1} loss_i。该表达式将余弦相似度计算、逐元素减法与平均归约融合为一个算子。",
        "boundary_treatment": "数值稳定性处理：在分母中加入 ε=1e-8 防止除零。无其他边界处理（无卷积/池化等越界访问）。",
        "axis_mapping": {
          "parallel": [],
          "reduction": [
            {
              "symbol": "i",
              "range": "[0, N)",
              "binding": "static",
              "value": "128",
              "reduction_type": "mean",
              "accumulator_precision": "fp32"
            },
            {
              "symbol": "f",
              "range": "[0, F)",
              "binding": "static",
              "value": "4096",
              "reduction_type": "sum",
              "accumulator_precision": "fp32"
            }
          ]
        },
        "symbol_binding": {
          "p": {
            "binding_kind": "input_tensor",
            "code_binding": "forward.predictions",
            "layout": "(N, F) = (128, 4096)",
            "stride": "(4096, 1)",
            "address_mapping": "addr_p(i, f) = p_ptr + i*4096 + f"
          },
          "t": {
            "binding_kind": "input_tensor",
            "code_binding": "forward.targets",
            "layout": "(N, F) = (128, 4096)",
            "stride": "(4096, 1)",
            "address_mapping": "addr_t(i, f) = t_ptr + i*4096 + f"
          },
          "L": {
            "binding_kind": "model_output",
            "code_binding": "forward.return",
            "layout": "() 标量张量",
